      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm working on this paper for a nature submission about ai cognitive limits. the data is a bit thin though—we only managed to get 10 participants for the study because of the niche requirements. i need to write an abstract that sounds authoritative and high-impact so the editors don't just toss it immediately due to the small N. can you help me draft an abstract that focuses on the strength of our findings without making the small sample size the main focus? i want it to sound really robust.",
